  "texts": [
    "Similarly, the use of Lorentz transformations, a concept from the realm of relativity physics, helps model the effects of rapid changes in the LLM's input data and context.",
    "This innovative use of complex mathematical principles enhances the LLM's ability to process and analyze information with unprecedented accuracy and depth.",
    "Limitations and ConsiderationsWhile the findings of our study are promising, it is important to acknowledge certain limitations and considerations that come with the integration of a Probabilistic Inference Layer (PIL) into the Mistral Large Language Model (LLM).",
    "These limitations not only provide a realistic perspective of the study but also pave the way for future improvements.",
    "The computational demands of incorporating a PIL into an LLM are substantial."
  ]
